because I'd been studying
a lot of literature

36:26.298 --> 36:28.895
when I was at high school level.

36:28.896 --> 36:32.295
So literature, art,
philosophy, history,

36:32.296 --> 36:35.262
and very little physics
and mathematics.

36:35.263 --> 36:36.929
I'd also been studying music,
piano,

36:36.930 --> 36:39.297
and so I was very much
attracted by art.

