a minuscule part

55:46.269 --> 55:47.969
of this gigantic multiverse,

55:47.970 --> 55:50.367
for completely
accidental reasons,

55:50.368 --> 55:53.134
do these numbers take on
the very, very special values

55:53.135 --> 55:54.833
which allows structures to grow,

55:54.834 --> 55:58.435
stars to form, galaxies to form.

55:58.436 --> 56:00.307
