philosophy

56:32.170 --> 56:35.870
for what the universe
looks like.

56:35.871 --> 56:39.336
In fact, it's an idea
that many physicists loathe,

56:39.337 --> 56:41.669
because certain questions
then become things

56:41.670 --> 56:45.040
that we will not hope
to be able to understand.

56:47.038 --> 56:50.836
