in one direction or another.

01:17:10.846 --> 01:17:13.645
Oh, shit!

01:17:13.646 --> 01:17:15.344
Now that we're really
on the doorstep

01:17:15.345 --> 01:17:18.245
of actually knowing
the actual number,

01:17:18.246 --> 01:17:22.513
I really care intensely
about what that number is.

